com.flurry.android.ads

Interface FlurryAdNativeListener


  • public interface FlurryAdNativeListener
    Listener for Native ads. The listener for Native ads. A listener is set of callback methods that allow a developer to manage and take actions within different phases of ad display.
    See Also:
    Flurry Publisher Support Site
